-- Towers Watson Promotes Kirkland Hicks to Be General Counsel
-- B y   S u s a n n a   P a k
-- 2012-09-13T13:12:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-13/towers-watson-promotes-kirkland-hicks-to-be-general-counsel.html
Towers Watson & Co. (TW) , the provider
of human-resource and consulting services, promoted Kirkland L.
Hicks to general counsel.  Hicks will replace Walter Bardenwerper, who is retiring at
the end of November after 25 years with the company, New York-
based Towers Watson said today in a statement distributed by
Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Susanna Pak in New York at 
 spak10@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
